/// Test group: amplifier envelope generator
/// Test purpose: amp eg all stages on MIDI cc
///
/// Test description:
/// Play repeatedly any note, while adjusting the following MIDI controls:
///
/// cc20: delay time, 0~10s
/// cc21: start level, 0~100%
/// cc22: attack time, 0~10s
/// cc23: hold time, 0~10s
/// cc24: decay time, 0~10s
/// cc25: sustain level, 0~100%
/// cc26: release time, 0~10s


